sentences.english: The invention discloses a method for detoxicating rapeseed cakes or rapeseed dregs.

sentences.english: A procedure for extracting amino acid from oil residue of cottonseed was introduced.

sentences.english: The residual oil in meals was blow 1%.

sentences.english: The major nutrients and nutritional value of double low rapeseed meal were described.

sentences.english: The development and feeding study of dehulled double-low rapeseed meal were introduced.

sentences.english: The regularity of extrusion parameters and residual oil rate were analyzed.
